# calligrawords

> Calligra's word processor application
> See also: calligrastage, calligrasheets, calligraflow
> More information: https://manned.org/calligrawords

- Launch the word processor application:

`calligrawords`

- Open a specific document:

`calligrawords {string value: path/to/document}`

- Display help or version:

`calligrawords --{string value: help|version}`
